headline: 5 Considerations In The Upcoming CPI Report
summary: Stock indices rallied despite limited CPI data last month; since then, small-caps and Dow are outperforming tech into early 2026.

headline: Is It Too Late To Consider FedEx (FDX) After Its Strong Recent Share Price Gains
summary: If you are wondering whether FedEx at around US$312 a share still offers value, you are not alone. This article is designed to help you frame that question clearly. The stock has recently posted returns of 6.6% over 7 days, 9.9% over 30 days, 6.6% year to date, 18.1% over 1 year, 76.6% over 3 years and 36.2% over 5 years.
